<li id="cite_note-61"><b><a href="#cite_ref-61" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://www.cnn.com/WORLD/9712/27/n.ireland.killing/" class="external text" title="http://www.cnn.com/WORLD/9712/27/n.ireland.killing/" rel="nofollow">"CNN - IRA splinter gang kills top Protestant guerrilla - December 27, 1997"</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.cnn.com/WORLD/9712/27/n.ireland.killing/" class="external free" title="http://www.cnn.com/WORLD/9712/27/n.ireland.killing/" rel="nofollow">http://www.cnn.com/WORLD/9712/27/n.ireland.killing/</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on November 19 2005</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=CNN+-+IRA+splinter+gang+kills+top+Protestant+guerrilla+-+December+27%2C+1997&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2FWORLD%2F9712%2F27%2Fn.ireland.killing%2F&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Guerrilla_warfare"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-62"><b><a href="#cite_ref-62" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://www.reuters.co.uk/newsPackageArticle.jhtml?type=topNews&amp;storyID=584330&amp;section=news" class="external text" title="http://www.reuters.co.uk/newsPackageArticle.jhtml?type=topNews&amp;storyID=584330&amp;section=news" rel="nofollow">"http://www.reuters.co.uk/newsPackageArticle.jhtml?type=topNews&amp;storyID=584330&amp;section=news"</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.reuters.co.uk/newsPackageArticle.jhtml?type=topNews&amp;storyID=584330&amp;section=news" class="external free" title="http://www.reuters.co.uk/newsPackageArticle.jhtml?type=topNews&amp;storyID=584330&amp;section=news" rel="nofollow">http://www.reuters.co.uk/newsPackageArticle.jhtml?type=topNews&amp;storyID=584330&amp;section=news</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on November 19 2005</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.co.uk%2FnewsPackageArticle.jhtml%3Ftype%3DtopNews%26storyID%3D584330%26section%3Dnews&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.co.uk%2FnewsPackageArticle.jhtml%3Ftype%3DtopNews%26storyID%3D584330%26section%3Dnews&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Guerrilla_warfare"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-63"><b><a href="#cite_ref-63" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.defencejournal.com/apr99/bangladesh.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.defencejournal.com/apr99/bangladesh.htm" rel="nofollow">WHY THE MOVEMENT FOR BANGLADESH SUCCEEDED: A military appreciation</a> by Mumtaz Iqbal</li>
<li id="cite_note-64"><b><a href="#cite_ref-64" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.canada.com/edmontonjournal/news/opinion/story.html?id=1db342f6-7872-4c39-8410-81ad3a916908&amp;k=25970" class="external text" title="http://www.canada.com/edmontonjournal/news/opinion/story.html?id=1db342f6-7872-4c39-8410-81ad3a916908&amp;k=25970" rel="nofollow">Reason to hope Canadians don't repeat history in Afghanistan</a>, Alan G. Jamieson, The Edmonton Journal, July 31 2006</li>
<li id="cite_note-65"><b><a href="#cite_ref-65" title="">^</a></b> See, for example, the guerilla operations in the <a href="/wiki/Cordillera" title="Cordillera">cordillera</a> of <a href="/wiki/Northern_Luzon" title="Northern Luzon" class="mw-redirect">Northern Luzon</a> lead by then-COL Russell Volckmann, United States Army, who escaped from Corregidor in the last hours before the capture of the rest of its military defenders, and who wrote a memoir, (1954) <i>[We Remained <a href="http://www.archive.org/stream/weremainedthreey011059mbp/weremainedthreey011059mbp_djvu.txt" class="external free" title="http://www.archive.org/stream/weremainedthreey011059mbp/weremainedthreey011059mbp_djvu.txt" rel="nofollow">http://www.archive.org/stream/weremainedthreey011059mbp/weremainedthreey011059mbp_djvu.txt</a>]</i>. Volckmann was later promoted a general.</li>
</ol>
</div>
